---
 CMakeLists.txt                                     | 14 --------------
 cmake/developer_package.cmake                      | 10 ++++++----
 .../ie_bridges/c/samples/common/CMakeLists.txt     |  2 ++
 inference-engine/samples/CMakeLists.txt            |  9 +++------
